2d49b8aed20b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFDA%20warns%20shoppers%20against%20eating%20Great%20Value%20frozen%20shrimp%20from%20Walmart%20due%20to%20possible%20exposure%20to%20Cesium-137.%3Cp%3ESiddharth%20Cavale%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFDA%20warns%20shoppers%20against%20eating%20frozen%20shrimp%20from%20Walmart%20due%20to%20possible%20exposure%20to%20Cesium-137.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20lots%20of%20frozen%20shrimp%20are%20affected%2C%20but%20all%20shipments%20from%20the%20distributor%20will%20be%20recalled.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECesium-137%20is%20a%20byproduct%20of%20nuclear%20fission%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20burns%20and%20acute%20radiation%20sickness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20want%20to%20put%20down%20your%20fork%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20is%20warning%20shoppers%20not%20to%20eat%2C%20sell%2C%20or%20serve%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-salary-data-revealed-how-much-tech-workers-make-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGreat%20Value%20raw%20frozen%20shrimp%3C%2Fa%3E%20sold%20at%20Walmart%20after%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20officials%20detected%20possible%20contamination%20from%20Cesium-137%2C%20a%20radioactive%20isotope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20recently%20purchased%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Falerts-advisories-safety-information%2Ffda-advises-public-not-eat-sell-or-serve-certain-imported-frozen-shrimp-indonesian-firm%23ProductDesc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eone%20of%20the%20impacted%20lots%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Great%20Value%20raw%20frozen%20shrimp%20from%20Walmart%2C%20throw%20it%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20FDA%20officials%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CBP%20initially%20flagged%20the%20presence%20of%20Cesium-137%20after%20screening%20shipping%20containers%20at%20four%20do