-prices-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGreat%20Value%20brand%20at%20Walmart%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20time%2C%20no%20product%20that%20has%20tested%20positive%20or%20alerted%20for%20Cesium-137%20(Cs-137)%20has%20entered%20the%20US%20commerce%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FDA%20wrote%2C%20although%20they%20recommend%20a%20recall%20for%20three%20Great%20Value%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20the%20shrimp%20become%20radioactive%3F%20Are%20all%20shrimp%20tested%20for%20radioactivity%3F%20Is%20foul%20play%20suspected%2C%20or%20is%20this%20some%20natural%20occurrence%3F%20These%20are%20questions%20I%20do%20not%20have%20answers%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20question%20I%20definitively%20know%20the%20answer%20to%20is%3A%20%3Cem%3EDo%20I%20want%20to%20eat%20the%20shrimp%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20yes%2C%20I%20do.%20I%20need%20to%20try%20it.%20I%20cannot%20resist%20knowing%20there's%20radioactive%20shrimp%20out%20there%20and%20that%20I%20could%20potentially%20harness%20its%20shrimpy%20powers.%20Would%20I%20get%20claws%3F%20A%20powerful%20tail%20to%20maneuver%20through%20water%3F%20Would%20I%20just%20go%20great%20with%20cocktail%20sauce%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%5BNote%3A%20Business%20Insider%20does%20not%20endorse%20eating%20anything%20radioactive%2C%20and%20you%20should%20not%20do%20this%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20tempting%20it%20sounds.%20Ingesting%20Cesium-137%20allows%20the%20radioactive%20material%20to%20accumulate%20in%20soft%20tissues%2C%20increasing%20cancer%20risk%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FDA.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20apparently%20the%20contaminated%20shipment%20was%20stopped%20before%20it%20hit%20shelves%2C%20it%20sounds%20like%20I'll%20never%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20find%20out.%20But%20thanks%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epower%20of%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20made%20a%20picture%20of%20myself%20as%20a%20radioactive%20shrimp%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cf